# Accepted misconfig IDs, one per line, each with its reason. Trivy picks this
# file up automatically from the scan root (the repo root, in security.yml).
# Convention mirrors collectiongeek-infra/.trivyignore.

# Workloads land in their namespace via the Argo CD Application's
# `destination.namespace` (argocd/*.yaml) — helm template output deliberately
# carries no metadata.namespace, so Trivy misreads it as "default".
AVD-KSV-0110
KSV-0110

# ghcr.io/collectiongeek is OUR registry: images are built and pushed only by
# this org's CI (app repo) and referenced by immutable per-env tags. Trivy's
# built-in trusted-registry list simply doesn't know it.
AVD-KSV-0125
KSV-0125
